headline: Medtronic (MDT) Declares US$0.71 Dividend Confirming 48 Years Of Increases
summary: Medtronic (MDT) has recently affirmed a Q2 dividend of $0.71 per share, which aligns with its commitment to long-standing dividend growth and underscores its stability as an S&P 500 Dividend Aristocrat. Over the last quarter, the company's share price rose by 6%, a performance roughly in line with broader market movements.
